<L>__{exterior festa streets moving view on fanucci night}
<A>__{walking through the crowded streets. the statue of san gennaro is arranged in some midnight religious ceremony. the view lifts up, to the rooftops.}
<L>__{exterior the rooftops night}
<A>__{vito makes the leap that separates two buildings; then crosses toward the large skylight in the center of the building.}
<L>__{exterior the streets night}
<A>__{the procession in the streets is preceded by ten altar boys; and the glittering monstrance, something of an altar carried out into the streets. the priest begins this nocturnal service, as the crowds in the street kneel down in prayer.}
<L>__{interior fanucci's building night}
<A>__{fanucci unlocks the door to his building; we can hear the services in the background.}
